BARS := "▰▰════════ 23%" "▰▰▰▰══════ 45%" "▰▰▰▰▰▰════ 62%" "▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰══ 78%" "▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰ 100%"

all: $(NAME)
	clear
	@for bar in $(BARS); do \
		echo "\033[1m\033[3m\033[5m\033[31m⋘  𝑃𝑙𝑒𝑎𝑠𝑒 𝑤𝑎𝑖𝑡... ⋙\033[0m"; \
		echo "\033[3m$$bar\033[0m"; \
		if [ "$$bar" = "▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰▰ 100%" ]; then \
			sleep 0.8; \
		else \
			sleep 0.5; \
		fi; \
		clear; \
	done
	clear;
